data.description: 4 Bedroom Home located just outside of town offering country living with city convenience just minutes away!  Amenities include covered front porch, living room, dining room, eat-in kitchen, family room featuring masonry fireplace, and half bath.  Two upper level bedrooms, and full bathroom.  Lower level bedroom, bathroom, and laundry room converted from 4th bedroom.  Basement includes nice space for storage, recreation, or hobby space.  Guest quarters offer living room/bedroom, kitchen, and bathroom.  2+-car attached garage with office/storage area, guest parking, plus additional storage sheds.  deck overlooks nice backyard and timber view.  Call  today!
